The paper deals with the application of deep reinforcement learning to the problem of autonomous driving, which is a multi-agent setting. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Robotics (cs.RO), and Machine Learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of trajectory planning and the importance of visual perception, which are relevant to the sub-categories of Computer Vision (cs.CV) and Systems and Control (cs.SY).
